title: IX509CertificateRequestPkcs10V3::get_AttestationEncryptionCertificate (certenroll.h)
description: The certificate used to encrypt the EKPUB and EKCERT values from the client. This property must be set to a valid certificate that chains to a trusted machine root. (Get)
